                </svg>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            "Very good training. I was able to learn JQL without any prior knowledge. I am now confident that I can apply customizable filters and create new dashboards for the teams I am managing. Thanks again."
          </p>
          <p class="font-bold text-[#1a1a1a]">Roy Reuben Sundaram</p>
